name: refrACTION (limited)
description: experimenting with an "accurate" light refractive glass material in blender 3d with cycles render engine made procedurally by separating rgb channels and indicating an index of refraction. each edition has a different index of refraction and thus bends the light uniquely. the categories from most to least scarce are: unique, scarce and limited.
